<view class="page-root">
  <view class="hero-mini">
    <view class="hero-mini-blob hero-mini-blob-1"></view>
    <view class="hero-mini-blob hero-mini-blob-2"></view>
    <view class="hero-mini-inner">
      <text class="hero-mini-kicker">设置</text>
      <text class="hero-mini-title">账号与安全</text>
      <text class="hero-mini-desc">管理账号风险操作，请谨慎处理注销等事项。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-accent"></view>
      <text class="section-title">危险操作</text>
    </view>
    <text class="section-desc">
      注销后将删除当前账号在本平台的资料与业务数据，且不可恢复。请确认已无未完成订单或纠纷后再操作。
    </text>
    <view class="danger-zone">
      <button
        class="danger-btn"
        hover-class="danger-btn-hover"
        hover-stay-time="70"
        bindtap="handleDeleteAccount"
        loading="{{deleting}}"
        disabled="{{deleting}}"
      >
        注销账号
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
